# Side quests for {{project_name}}

Concepts you don't fully grok yet. Captured at three moments:

- **Automatic during cutting** — agent flags when it uses a concept you didn't engage with in the plan
- **Automatic during planning** — `/plan-side-quests` scans the finished plan for unfamiliar concepts
- **Manual** — `/sq <concept>` command, ~5 seconds

Closures via `/sq close SQ-NNN` after a learning session. Entries stay in this file forever — track learning over time.

## Format per entry

```
## SQ-NNN: <concept>
- **Captured:** <YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM>
- **Where:** <plan section, file, conversation context>
- **What I don't get:** <one-line>
- **Status:** open | done
- **Resources collected:**
  - [ ] <link or note>
- **What I now understand:** <filled at closure>
```

